“Any chance you’ll be at a park today swangin’ maces?” 

Me: “Yep!” 

I’m nothing if not consistent!  And my friends know it :)

On Saturday, I had the serendipitous pleasure of hosting @mytrainercarmen & @cordellk1 at The Parthenon for some kettlebell juggling, mace and rope flow.  In about 2 hours we had a short clinic on all three implements and had the pleasure of entertaining a few visitors as well! (Just look at the way the little ones are watching Carmen 😇)

Anyhow, now I’m even more stoked for the upcoming @functionalkettlebelltraining cert next weekend 😁💪🏻💫
